data.description: Contract Pending Welcome to your dream home! This charming residence, nestled on a spacious corner lot, boasts a perfect blend of comfort and style. With three bedrooms and three bathrooms, there's room for the whole family. Step inside to discover the allure of new flooring and carpet on the main level, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.The recently updated bathrooms add a touch of modern luxury, while the interior walls showcase a fresh coat of paint, providing a clean and contemporary aesthetic. The oversized garage offers ample space for vehicles and storage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – schedule your private showing today and envision a life of comfort and elegance in this meticulously maintained property.
